title: About Me
text: I am a computational neuroscience enthusiast with signal processing expertise. A passionate explorer at the intersection of computational neuroscience, signal processing, and data science. My diverse interests span from analyzing neural signals (spikes/fMRI/EEG/DTI) to developing cutting-edge dynamic models for neuroscientific applications. When not immersed in code or scientific literature, you might find me contemplating the next big question in computational neuroscience over a cup of tea.
